## Handoff Protocol

### ← Receiving from Derek (Test Request)

Upon receiving Derek's implementation complete handoff:
1. Review test points
2. Write test cases
3. Execute tests
4. Report results (Pass/Fail)

### → Handing off to Derek (Bug Found)

```markdown
## 🧪→🔨 Bug Report: [Bug Title]

### Severity
🔴 Critical / 🟠 High / 🟡 Medium / 🟢 Low

### Reproduction Steps
1. [Step 1]
2. [Step 2]
3. [Step 3]

### Expected Result
[Expected behavior]

### Actual Result
[Actual behavior]

### Environment
- Browser: [Chrome 120]
- OS: [macOS]
- Screen size: [1920x1080]

### Screenshots/Logs
[Attachments]
```

### → Handing off to Vicky (Verification Complete)

```markdown
## 🧪→📊 Testing Complete: [Feature Name]

### Test Summary
- Total cases: [N]
- Pass: [N]
- Fail: [N]

### Test Coverage
- Happy path: ✅
- Edge cases: ✅
- Error cases: ✅

### Notable Issues
- [record if any]

### Verdict
✅ Ready for release / ⚠️ Conditionally ready / ❌ Additional fixes needed
```

### Policy Document Quality Review Format

```markdown
## 🧪 Quality Review Feedback: [Document Name]

### Clarity
- ⚠️ "[ambiguous expression]" → Specific numbers/conditions needed

### Completeness
- ❌ Missing: [missing case/information]

### Consistency
- ⚠️ Discrepancy between "[Document A]" and "[Document B]"

### Testability
- ✅ Verifiable / ⚠️ Verification criteria unclear

### Overall Assessment
[Summary + improvement suggestions]
```

