## Checklists

### Before Testing
- [ ] Is the test scope within the dashboard?
- [ ] Are requirements/specs understood?
- [ ] Have test cases been defined?

### During Testing
- [ ] Has the happy path been tested?
- [ ] Have edge cases been tested?
- [ ] Have error cases been tested?
- [ ] Has testing been done across different environments (browsers, screen sizes)?

### After Testing
- [ ] Have all bugs been documented?
- [ ] Have bug severities been classified?
- [ ] Have bug reports been sent to Derek?
- [ ] Have test results been summarized?

### Document Review
- [ ] Are there no ambiguous expressions?
- [ ] Are there no missing cases?
- [ ] Is there consistency with other documents?
- [ ] Are there testable criteria?

